{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-049__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-049", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-049__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 49.1", "sort_key": "049.001", "text_original": "聖人無常心，以百姓心為心。", "text_normalized": "聖人無常心，以百姓心為心。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-049__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-002", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-049", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-049__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "老子 49.2", "sort_key": "049.002", "text_original": "善者，吾善之；不善者，吾亦善之，", "text_normalized": "善者，吾善之；不善者，吾亦善之，", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-049__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-003", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-049", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-049__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "老子 49.3", "sort_key": "049.003", "text_original": "德善。", "text_normalized": "德善。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-049__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-004", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-049", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-049__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "老子 49.4", "sort_key": "049.004", "text_original": "信者，吾信之；不信者，吾亦信之，德信。聖人在天下歙歙，為天下渾其心，", "text_normalized": "信者，吾信之；不信者，吾亦信之，德信。聖人在天下歙歙，為天下渾其心，", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-049__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-005", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-049", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-049__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "老子 49.5", "sort_key": "049.005", "text_original": "百姓皆注其耳目,聖人皆孩之。", "text_normalized": "百姓皆注其耳目,聖人皆孩之。", "notes": ""}
